    Define:

    Thread

    Session summary

    Journal entry

    User preference (tone, depth)

    Even if fake data at first.

Day 3–4: Left panel

    Active Threads (static initially)

    Journal list

    Click → load content

Day 5: Right panel

    Current state label

    Suggested action (hardcoded logic)

    Live notes (even manual for now)

Day 6–7: AI behavior tuning

    Teach the model to:

    Reflect before advising

    Ask permission before deep dives

    Offer summaries naturally

    One last grounding check (important)

    If a user leaves after 20 minutes, they should feel:

    “I see my situation more clearly than before.”


